From Kevin Stamber Subject Re How difficult is it to get Penguin tickets In article Dean R Money writes The subject line says it Is it terribly difficult to get tickets to Penguins games especially now that they are in the playoffs Would it be easy to find scalpers outside of the Igloo selling tickets Dean Money Here is my traditional experience with tickets playoffs and otherwise at the Civic Scalping is illegal but nonetheless present outside the Best strategy given that you don't mind missing the Anthem which is OK if Taylor decides to come back ever again is to wait until or when the game is rolling the scalpers are at this point desperate to sell and will reduce to near or at face value to get rid of their Playoffs are a little different in that good seats will go early on what's left at may be nosebleed material D E sections Others can add on their opinions as Kevin Stamber Purdue University PENGUINS DEVILS Pens lead series game to none